    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jsdalli ( to ) starp ſepti-\nneem/ jeb arri starp astoxeem/ jo\ntu ne finnt kahds Launums buhs\nwirs Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad tahs Badebbezis pil-\nnas irr/ tad teletj tahs fitpru\nLeetu us to Semint/ un ka tas\nKohksprett Deenas-Widdn/ jeb\nprett Seemeta- Puſti krittihſ /\ntar Weetâ/ kur wiꞥſch krittihſ /\ntur wiꞥſch paliks.\n"
