      "column": "right",
      "text": "Itt ka tu ne finni/ ka\nZeſsch ta Wehja irr/ jeb tee\nKault irr eekſch greuhtas\nwas Meeſahm/ tapatt neſ\ntu to Deewa Darbu/ kas to\nfu darra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rihta fehjt tawu Seh-\nun ne atrauji tawu Rohku A\nkarâ/ jo tu ne finni/ kurſch va\nfi isdohtees/ woj tchtin jeb ta\nun kaut abbejahds Rohpa la\nisdohtohs/ tad buhtu tas jo\nbaks.\n"
