      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Japrohjam tas Gattchu-\nirr talde/ un Azzim tikkanis\nSauli uhſluhkoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr/ jepſchu tas\nweks dauds Gaddus dshwo/\neektch ta wiffa preezajahs/ tad\nwiꞥſch arri atminn tahs Deen\ntahs Tumfibus/ jo winno bn\ndauds/ un wiff/ kas pagahj\nirr/ tas irr Neceetiba.\n"
    },
